    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In anno dominice incarnationis millesimo centesimo duodecimo, quarto kalend.
                        madi, indictione quinta. Manifestus sum ego <persName><name
                                ref="Bernarduccius">Bernarduccius</name></persName> filius olim
                                <persName><name ref="Signorellus de Bozano"
                            >Signorelli</name></persName> di <placeName ref="#places/3222"
                            >Bocano</placeName> et per hanc cartulam, pro anime mee remedio, dono et
                        offero (…) Deo et <rs key="#Hospitals">hospityo</rs> illo (…) in loco qui
                        nuncupatur <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Churches #Hospitals"
                            >Tepasco</placeName> et <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206"
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti
                            Gilii et Sancti Iacobi Apostoli</orgName> due petye terre aratoria iuris
                        mei <foreign>che si trovano a</foreign> Campum Boiani. Una petia dicitur
                        Lacium ad Portum Omnipilie. Est per mensuram iustam cultra una (…). Caput
                        unum tenet in terra <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3213">Sancti
                            Laurenti</orgName>, aliud caput tenet in padule, latus unum tenet in
                        terra filii <persName><name ref="Centius">Centi</name></persName> et filii
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> (…). Alia
                        petya <foreign>si trova</foreign> ibi prope, est per mensuram iusta cultra
                        una. <foreign>Ha il primo capo confinante con</foreign> via della cuna, que
                        pergit ad portum, aliud caput tenet in terra filiorum <persName><name
                                ref="Bellinus">Bellini</name></persName>, latus unum tenet in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio">Ugiccionis</name></persName> (…),
                        aliud latus tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Anicius"
                            >Anici</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Hugolinus"
                                >Ugolini</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Hughicio de Camigliano">Ugiccionis</name> de <placeName
                                ref="#places/3245">Camulgano</placeName></persName>. (…) Actum in
                        predicto loco Bocani in domo predicti Bernarducci.</ab>
